model.name: Millard2020 - Kinetic model of Glucose and Acetate metabolisms in E. coli

body.p: Calibrated kinetic model of glucose and acetate metabolisms of Escherichia coli, as detailed in Millard et al., 2020 (DOI: 10.1101/2020.08.18.255356).

body.pre:
dilution rate (in h-1), used to simulate chemostat experiment
default value: 0

feed (in mmolGlc/h-1), used to simulate chemostat experiment
default value: 0

biomass concentration at which a 30mM acetate pulse it performed
default value: 10000 (i.e., no pulse)
